OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FFine into
OL,6,Fthe evening, with some late sunshine
OL,7,Fgiving way to overnight clear periods,
OL,8,Falthough perhaps becoming cloudier in
OL,9,Fthe west later. Winds gradually
OL,10,Feasing, with a slight grass frost
OL,11,Fdeveloping in one or two prone rural
OL,12,Fareas.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FA fine start, eventually very
OL,15,Fwarm with sunshine. Cloudier
OL,16,Fconditions and some rain or showers
OL,17,Fwill make gradual inroads from the
OL,18,Fwest later, perhaps culminating in
OL,19,Fsome thundery showers locally.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
