OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMore
OL,6,Funsettled than recently, with rain or
OL,7,Fshowers, some thundery. Gradually
OL,8,Fturning cooler. Sunny spells remain
OL,9,Fpossible, but also showers, these
OL,10,Fshowers becoming lighter and further
OL,11,Fbetween into next week.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
